parameters:
Anomalocaris: Mmph, mmph... I doubt even the Shark Duke
would want a rematch after this... It's my complete victory!
Don't you think so, Shark Broccoli?

Anomalocaris: I'll even cut costs on the hustle you guys had
before... Reduce the amount per bag of the delicious powder
by 5%! Also, mix in some wheat flour to bulk it up...

Memimi: Don't joke around!! The delicious powder developed
by Shark Broccoli's boss is a complete food, considering
both taste and health!!

Memimi: Adding unnecessary stuff or reducing the quantity is
nothing short of blasphemy against the boss...! It's
absolutely unforgivable!!

Memimi: It's a rematch, Anomalocaris!! I won't lose this
time... I'll protect both the organization and the delicious
powder!!

Shark Broccoli: Shark Duke, that's enough... Stop, just
stop...

Anomalocaris: Mmph mmph mmph... You still have the energy to
fight again? Even if you come back for more, you'll just
lose again~ It's just adding insult to injury!

Memimi has already completed a nightmarish task to fight
Anomalocaris, walking around the city completely naked while
masturbating.

Henchman: Is she freaking insane? She got made to masturbate
naked in front of everyone in town, and she still wants to
go through that again even though she knows she can't win?

Henchman: We all took photos of her playing with her
hairless pussy! What's next, an even more extreme task? Can
she handle it?

In monster fights, those who are defeated must complete any
one condition set by their opponent if they want a
rematch... Memimi has been tormented by this rule more than
anyone could imagine.

After all, she was forced to expose herself naked and
masturbate while walking a long distance within her own
living area. She was seen by classmates and subordinates in
a state she never wanted to show anyone, and it was even
recorded. Even now, it's whispered about in the streets and
the academy, and she writhes in embarrassment every day
remembering it.

The next condition might be even worse... Yet despite her
inner terror, Memimi has no choice but to say...

Memimi: As if I was embarrassed at all! I can laugh off any
condition you guys come up with every single time!! That
means I can challenge you again and again... I'm always
ready for battle!!

Anomalocaris: You're thick-skinned, that's for sure... Next
time, I'll give you a condition so vile you'll shake and
refuse!

Memimi: (Please stop... The last one already far exceeded
what I could handle! Somehow... Ah!)

Memimi: Huh... I'll give you one piece of advice... If it's
something embarrassing or lewd, it won't break my spirit...
You should try something else...

Anomalocaris: No, we're sticking with masturbation!! Now
that it's come to this, I'll make sure to embarrass you
completely for a total victory!!

The cringe-worthy meeting continued, and a dreadful
condition was imposed on Memimi...
//全体マップの試合会場での行先を試合3に変更
'戦え何度でも！アノマロカリスモスマンと再再戦の巻'

Anomalocaris: What are you going to do if you don't forgive
me? You're just a lowly underling who lost to me twice!!

Memimi: (I want to challenge him to a rematch and stop
this... But now is not the time to act rashly...)
Memimi decided to back down for the time being...
